icular, we find that U=\\phi is optimal and the\nboundary of the rate-equivocation region is achieved by varying V alone for the\nBSC-BEC wiretap channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2011 19:07:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-10-21"}
