08, A&A 478, 235). Given the lack of\nconstraints on the surface composition of Ceres, however, we cannot assert the\ncauses of these variations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2011 07:19:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
