rolonging of the connection to the spinor bundle with\neven-dimensional base are considered, and the corresponding curvature spinors\nare constructed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2011 09:27:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 31 Dec 2011 18:00:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 May 2012 13:14:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-05-11"}
