h some flares showing\nlonger (10-18 s) delays. The former are consistent with energy transfer along\nthe flaring loop legs by non-thermal electron beams, the latter to the passage\nof conduction fronts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2011 10:53:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
